OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with some sunshine, though
OL,7,Fcloudier towards the north coast.
OL,8,FOvernight staying dry with clear
OL,9,Fspells in the east while parts of the
OL,10,Fwest will turn cloudier.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FIt will remain dry and very
OL,13,Fwarm with variable amounts of cloud
OL,14,Fand some bright or sunny spells.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FGenerally
OL,17,Fcloudier on Friday, especially the
OL,18,Fnorthwest, with a chance of some rain.
OL,19,FA dry weekend with bright or sunny
OL,20,Fspells and variable amounts of cloud.
OL,21,FVery warm or hot.
